  • fgeo

Data from SCBI.

Source: R/data.R
scbi.Rd

  • scbi_tree1 and scbi_species are complete tree and species tables from SCBI.

  • scbi_stem_shrub_tiny and scbi_stem_tree_tiny are small example datasets containing exclusively shrubs and trees.

scbi_tree1

scbi_species

scbi_stem_shrub_tiny

scbi_stem_tree_tiny

Format

Objects of class tbl_df (inherit from tbl, data.frame). See structure in Examples.

Source

http://bit.ly/scbi-forestgeo-data
